    "The primary goal for students using AI appears to enhance efficiency and boost productivity.",
    "This is particularly evident when they employ AI in entrepreneurial activities.",
    "7% of students expressed that they would continue to use AI when they start their own businesses, where they may have to work in small teams with limited manpower in the early stage.",
